		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_BREWERY_PEDIA">
			<Text>A brewery is a dedicated building for the making of beer, generally for trade or sale to the public. Beer is one of the oldest beverages humans have produced, dating back to at least the 5th millennium BC and recorded in the written history of Ancient Egypt and Mesopotamia.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]--Wikipedia</Text>
